abstract: SA3 based data for Language spoken at home by Sex, for 2011 Census. Count of all persons on Census night based on place of usual residence. This list of languages consists of the most common Language Spoken at Home responses reported in the 2006 Census. Data sourced from: http://www.abs.gov.au/census. For further information about these and related statistics, contact the National Information and Referral Services on 1300 135 070. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
